This is a test-bundle for the experimental form support.

It is very early status and will be finalized as a demo example over the weekend.

Distribution: Best used with Symfony Standard Edition

Requirements:

Symfony has to be loaded from bschussek's experimental branch (github.com/bschussek/symfony/tree/experimental)

Installation:
=============

1. Add Bundle to Kernel
2. Add AcmePizzaBundle to Doctrine ORM Mappings
3. Create Database + Database Schema (4 tables)
4. Register AcmePizzaBundle/Resources/config/routing.yml in app/config/routing.yml

Use:
====

Go to app_dev.php/pizza


